.TH CALIBRATION_X11 1

.SH NAME
calibration_x11 \- fullscreen Tobii eye tracker calibration for X11

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B calibration_x11

.SH DESCRIPTION
Fullscreen X11 calibration utility for Tobii eye trackers.

Creates a 3x3 calibration mesh and stores the result in:

.B ~/.local/tobii_4c/calx11.conf

Used together with:

.B eye_mouse_x11

Features:
.IP
- fullscreen calibration
.IP
- dynamic screen resolution
.IP
- retry handling
.IP
- gaze validation
.IP
- standalone operation

.SH FILES
.TP
.B calx11.conf
Calibration mesh configuration.

.SH AUTHOR
Uwe Niethammer
